class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3327470/extras/c3dcb2cf0bbe8b94cd1c6d217765c9c6.avif?t=1743188373\" width=600 height=100 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >获得电影版权并设置放映时间的顺序。游戏中最详细的系统——电影排片系统，为你提供了多种策略机会。你可以设定高价播放热门电影，或者以低价吸引更多观众。可以尝试多种组合！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3327470/extras/e3d846a01010e3f45af3f88aace15b77.poster.avif?t=1743188373\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3327470/extras/e3d846a01010e3f45af3f88aace15b77.webm?t=1743188373\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3327470/extras/e3d846a01010e3f45af3f88aace15b77.mp4?t=1743188373\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3327470/extras/e922b7376e5e916b245883cf2e09a05e.avif?t=1743188373\" width=600 height=100 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >通过为你的影院购买新物品，可以增加存储空间、视觉吸引力和功能性。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3327470/extras/a6abdbc19de66be8aa9cb97f6f7badbc.poster.avif?t=1743188373\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3327470/extras/a6abdbc19de66be8aa9cb97f6f7badbc.webm?t=1743188373\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3327470/extras/a6abdbc19de66be8aa9cb97f6f7badbc.mp4?t=1743188373\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
